      "raw_text": "Even after the macOS GPU process landed on release (in FF 146), crashes continue to happen in the parent process in threads whose name includes \"Renderer\". Does this surprise anyone?\n\nhttps://crash-stats.mozilla.org/search/?crashing_thread_name=~Renderer&process_type=parent&process_type=parent&version=146&version=146.0.1&version=147&version=147.0.1&version=147.0.2&version=148&version=149&platform=Mac%20OS%20X&date=%3E%3D2025-10-29T17%3A25%3A00.000Z&date=%3C2026-01-29T17%3A25%3A00.000Z&_facets=signature&_facets=version&_facets=crashing_thread_name&_sort=-date&_columns=date&_columns=signature&_columns=product&_columns=version&_columns=build_id&_columns=platform#facet-signature\n\nDumb question, I'm sure. But I'm probably not the only one puzzled.",
      "creator": "smichaud@pobox.com",
      "creation_time": "2026-01-29T17:19:26Z",
      "bug_id": 1993123,
      "text": "Even after the macOS GPU process landed on release (in FF 146), crashes continue to happen in the parent process in threads whose name includes \"Renderer\". Does this surprise anyone?\n\nhttps://crash-stats.mozilla.org/search/?crashing_thread_name=~Renderer&process_type=parent&process_type=parent&version=146&version=146.0.1&version=147&version=147.0.1&version=147.0.2&version=148&version=149&platform=Mac%20OS%20X&date=%3E%3D2025-10-29T17%3A25%3A00.000Z&date=%3C2026-01-29T17%3A25%3A00.000Z&_facets=signature&_facets=version&_facets=crashing_thread_name&_sort=-date&_columns=date&_columns=signature&_columns=product&_columns=version&_columns=build_id&_columns=platform#facet-signature\n\nDumb question, I'm sure. But I'm probably not the only one puzzled.",
